tests = int(input())
for i in range(tests):
    length = int(input())
    arr = list(map(int, input().split()))
    limit = max(arr) * 10
    ans = 0
    multiples_arr = []
    for j in arr:
        x = 1
        while j * x < limit:
            multiples_arr.append(j * x)
            x += 1
    multiples_arr.sort()
    ans = max(ans, multiples_arr[0])
    for x in range(1, len(multiples_arr)):
        ans = max(ans, multiples_arr[x] - multiples_arr[x - 1])
    print(ans)
